      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be made roadworthy. The exterior shows substantial rust on the lower panels, multiple large dents, and significant paint oxidation. Under the hood, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate repair, while the interior has heavy wear, including torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. It is best suited as a project car or for parts.",
